						<p class="semibold">
Can I customize the text message response?
						</p>
						<p>
Yes, that's the whole point of SMS Autoresponders, which is why Tatango gives you the full 160 characters of the text message to do with what you want. Seriously, put whatever you want in the response, we don't care!
						</p>
						
						<p class="semibold">
How many Autoresponder campaigns can I create?
						</p>
